0 DOMINATE~
[*]      Command - Allows you to give the target a single word command.
[**]     Mesmerize - Allows you to give multiple word commands.
[***]    Conditioning - Target is unable to resist dominate or attack you.
[****]   Possession - Allows you to control a mob.
[*****]  Obedience - No speech or eye contact for command.
[******] Mob Rule - Command are usable on 'all'.
[*******] Commands work through willpower.

