[**]     Spiriteyes - Allows the vampire to see into the umbra.
[***]    Preserve - Stops corpses from decaying.
[****]   Spiritgate - Makes a gate to the killer of a corpse.
[*****]  Spiritguardian - Summons a guardian to warn you of danger.
[******] Zombie - Creates an Undead subject from a corpse.
[*******]Torment - Allows the user to directly attack a spirit.

